00:00:25.130 --> 00:00:28.910 align:middle line:10%
But this particular
day, it was October.

00:00:28.910 --> 00:00:31.280 align:middle line:90%
It was chilly.

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:34.650 align:middle line:84%
And I kind of felt like
