But I had enough money to
get her a healthy lunch.

00:01:34.380 --> 00:01:36.210 align:middle line:84%
So we went to a
health food store.

00:01:36.210 --> 00:01:38.400 align:middle line:84%
And I was all proud
that no one else

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:41.790 align:middle line:84%
would know that I was on welfare
because I was in this really

00:01:41.790 --> 00:01:42.990 align:middle line:90%
nice health food store.

00:01:42.990 --> 00:01:43.902 align:middle line:90%
And we bought lunch.

00:01:43.902 --> 00:01:45.360 align:middle line:84%
And we went up into
the food court.

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:46.460 align:middle line:90%
And I'm sitting there.

00:01:46.460 --> 00:01:47.460 align:middle line:90%
